<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="vi">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>SmartSpend AI</title>
    <link href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.0/dist/css/bootstrap.min.css" rel="stylesheet">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap-icons@1.11.0/font/bootstrap-icons.css">
    <style>
        :root { --sidebar-width: 260px; }
        body { background-color: #f0f2f5; font-family: 'Inter', sans-serif; overflow-x: hidden; }
        
        /* Sidebar Style */
        .sidebar {
            width: var(--sidebar-width);
            height: 100vh;
            position: fixed;
            left: 0; top: 0;
            background: white;
            border-right: 1px solid #e5e7eb;
            z-index: 1000;
            padding: 1.5rem;
        }
        
        .main-content {
            margin-left: var(--sidebar-width);
            padding: 2rem;
            min-height: 100vh;
        }

        .nav-link {
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            padding: 0.8rem 1rem;
            color: #4b5563;
            border-radius: 12px;
            margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
            transition: all 0.3s;
        }

        .nav-link:hover, .nav-link.active {
            background-color: #0d6efd;
            color: white !important;
        }

        .nav-link i { margin-right: 12px; font-size: 1.2rem; }

        @media (max-width: 768px) {
            .sidebar { transform: translateX(-100%); transition: 0.3s; }
            .main-content { margin-left: 0; }
            .sidebar.active { transform: translateX(0); }
        }

        @keyframes pulse-red {
            0% { transform: scale(0.95); box-shadow: 0 0 0 0 rgba(255, 82, 82, 0.7); }
            70% { transform: scale(1); box-shadow: 0 0 0 15px rgba(255, 82, 82, 0); }
            100% { transform: scale(0.95); box-shadow: 0 0 0 0 rgba(255, 82, 82, 0); }
        }

        .recording {
            animation: pulse-red 1.5s infinite;
            background-color: #ff5252 !important;
            color: white !important;
        }

        .btn-action {
            transition: all 0.2s ease;
            cursor: pointer;
            border-radius: 16px !important;
        }
        .btn-action:hover {
            transform: translateY(-5px);
            filter: brightness(1.1);
        }
        .btn-action:active {
            transform: scale(0.95);
        }

        .transaction-item {
            border-radius: 16px;
            transition: all 0.2s;
        }
        .transaction-item:hover {
            background-color: #f8f9fa;
            transform: translateX(5px);
        }
        .bg-danger-subtle { background-color: #fee2e2; }
        .bg-success-subtle { background-color: #d1fae5; }
        .transaction-actions { opacity: 0; transition: 0.3s; }
        .transaction-item:hover .transaction-actions { opacity: 1; }
        .cursor-pointer { cursor: pointer; }

        #notificationBell {
            cursor: pointer;
            transition: transform 0.2s ease;
        }

        #notificationBell:hover {
            transform: scale(1.1);
        }

        .dropdown-item:active {
            background-color: transparent !important;
            color: black !important;
        }

        .bg-warning-subtle { background-color: #fff3cd; }
        .bg-info-subtle { background-color: #cff4fc; }

        .dropdown-menu .dropdown-item {
            white-space: normal !important; /* Cho phép chữ tự động xuống dòng */
            word-wrap: break-word;
        }

        .dropdown-item:hover {
            background-color: #f8f9fa !important;
        }

        /* Tùy chỉnh thanh cuộn cho bảng thông báo (nếu nhiều tin quá) */
        div::-webkit-scrollbar {
            width: 6px;
        }
        div::-webkit-scrollbar-thumb {
            background: #e0e0e0;
            border-radius: 10px;
        }

        div::-webkit-scrollbar {
            width: 6px;
        }
        div::-webkit-scrollbar-thumb {
            background: #e0e0e0;
            border-radius: 10px;
        }
        .bg-warning-subtle { background-color: #fff3cd !important; }
        .bg-info-subtle { background-color: #cff4fc !important; }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="sidebar">
        <div class="d-flex align-items-center mb-4 px-2">
            <i class="bi bi-wallet2 text-primary fs-3 me-2"></i>
            <span class="fw-bold fs-4">SmartSpend</span>
        </div>

        
        
        <nav class="nav flex-column">
            <a href="/dashboard" class="nav-link <%= typeof path !== 'undefined' && path === 'dashboard' ? 'active' : '' %>">
                <i class="bi bi-grid-1x2-fill"></i> Tổng quan
            </a>
            <a href="/dashboard/history" class="nav-link <%= typeof path !== 'undefined' && path === 'history' ? 'active' : '' %>">
                <i class="bi bi-clock-history"></i> Lịch sử thu chi
            </a>
            <a href="/dashboard/profile" class="nav-link <%= typeof path !== 'undefined' && path === 'profile' ? 'active' : '' %>">
                <i class="bi bi-person-circle"></i> Tài khoản của tôi
            </a>
            
            <hr>
            <a href="/auth/logout" class="nav-link text-danger">
                <i class="bi bi-box-arrow-left"></i> Đăng xuất
            </a>
        </nav>
    </div>

    <div class="main-content">
        <div class="d-flex justify-content-end align-items-center mb-4 border-bottom pb-3">
            <div class="dropdown">
                <div class="position-relative cursor-pointer" id="notificationBell" data-bs-toggle="dropdown" aria-expanded="false" style="cursor: pointer;">
                    <i class="bi bi-bell-fill fs-4 text-secondary"></i>
                    <span class="position-absolute top-0 start-100 translate-middle p-1 bg-danger border border-light rounded-circle">
                        <span class="visually-hidden">New alerts</span>
                    </span>
                </div>
                
                <ul class="dropdown-menu dropdown-menu-end shadow border-0 p-0 mt-3" aria-labelledby="notificationBell" style="width: 400px; border-radius: 16px; overflow: hidden;">
                    <li class="bg-primary text-white p-3 d-flex justify-content-between align-items-center">
                        <span class="fw-bold">Thông báo mới nhất</span>
                        <span class="badge bg-white text-primary rounded-pill">2</span>
                    </li>
                    
                    <div style="max-height: 400px; overflow-y: auto;">
                        <li>
                            <div class="dropdown-item p-3 border-bottom d-flex align-items-start shadow-none" style="white-space: normal;">
                                <div class="bg-warning-subtle text-warning p-2 rounded-3 me-3">
                                    <i class="bi bi-exclamation-triangle-fill fs-5"></i>
                                </div>
                                <div>
                                    <p class="mb-1 small fw-bold text-dark">Cảnh báo hạn mức!</p>
                                    <p class="mb-0 text-muted small lh-base">
                                        Ný ơi, ný đã tiêu hết **85%** tiền tháng này rồi đó. Hệ thống khuyên ný nên giảm chi tiêu ăn uống lại nhé.
                                    </p>
                                </div>
                            </div>
                        </li>

                        <li>
                            <div class="dropdown-item p-3 border-bottom d-flex align-items-start shadow-none" style="white-space: normal;">
                                <div class="bg-info-subtle text-info p-2 rounded-3 me-3">
                                    <i class="bi bi-lightbulb-fill fs-5"></i>
                                </div>
                                <div>
                                    <p class="mb-1 small fw-bold text-dark">Gợi ý từ trợ lý AI</p>
                                    <p class="mb-0 text-muted small lh-base">
                                        Tháng này ný đi trà sữa hơi nhiều (5 lần). Bớt lại một chút là ný có thêm tiền tiết kiệm rồi đó!
                                    </p>
                                </div>
                            </div>
                        </li>
                    </div>

                    <li>
                        <a class="dropdown-item text-center py-3 small text-primary fw-bold bg-light" href="#">Xem tất cả thông báo</a>
                    </li>
                </ul>
            </div>
        </div>